        {
            "title": "薄扶林道綠van越線撞倒過路老婦 重創昏迷送院 地面遺血路",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"專線小巴撞倒婆婆。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c4788c8f0313a5ae7af80d4fcbadf418/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030111062429413.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">專線小巴撞倒婆婆。楊偉亨攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西半山薄扶林道近置富路13-19號網球場對開，今（1日）早上8時49分，上址正進行道路工程，安排單線雙程行車，一部專線小巴，往薄扶林花園方向行駛，司機見工程人員指示可行車，遂駛越對面線，期間一名老婦橫過馬路，遭小巴車頭撞倒，頭部淌血，昏迷送院搶救，路面遺下一條長血路。警方正調查意外原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111255/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"路面遺下一條長血路。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/58aa545ca7d5db4b075a748a74212ecf/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        路面遺下一條長血路。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111256/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3ccbb16b4caa2eb010a666cd7266adb0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111257/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場正進行道路工程，安排單線雙程行車。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e36f79ebe9ec7abf4b673028d99bab93/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場正進行道路工程，安排單線雙程行車。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111258/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場正進行道路工程，安排單線雙程行車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/907d8f417c4985cca22fee05748ae31e/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場正進行道路工程，安排單線雙程行車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111259/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"道路工程職員在場協查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28de7b63802aa8f0ebb87a493291f3dd/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        道路工程職員在場協查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111260/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場遺下血路。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/94b1fd99ddf7d38f5d0794ad7298510d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場遺下血路。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111261/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"稍後小巴被拖走扣驗。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/23cd32281c4ef214e92aeafa13262adf/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_104359252_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        稍後小巴被拖走扣驗。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
