        {
            "title": "荃灣青山公路的士撞九巴後剷上石壆花槽 男司機女乘客一度被困獲救",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"的士剷上石壆花槽，女乘客一度被困車廂獲救送院。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/976b432d8f3a76a6fdd322757002a5c9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030110194350412.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">的士剷上石壆花槽，女乘客一度被困車廂獲救送院。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今(1日)早上8時35分，荃灣青山公路四線行車往葵涌方向，事發時一部載客的士，沿第四線行駛，只可右轉入西樓角街，但的士司機並沒有右轉，反而直駛 ，撞向前面Ｅ31路線九巴，的士之後剷上右邊石壆花槽始停，巴士右邊車身近尾部遭撞爛，年約60歲的士男司機及女乘客一度被困車廂，稍後消防接報到場，將兩人救出，俱輕傷送院，警方正調查意外原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111203/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士剷上石壆花槽，女乘客一度被困車廂獲救送院。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/941133861c3d66e6432bb007beb232ab/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_094813363_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的士剷上石壆花槽，女乘客一度被困車廂獲救送院。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111204/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e473eb8a816f7228e2fe3ba3573d4cac/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_094813363_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</d